"|checkbox| Allows :ref:`features in-place modification "
"<processing_inplace_edit>` of point features"
msgstr ""
"|checkbox| Permet :ref:`la modification de la couche source "
"<processing_inplace_edit>` pour des entités de type point"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:784
msgid ":ref:`qgispointonsurface`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgispointonsurface`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:802
msgid "**Create centroid for each part**"
msgstr "**Créez un centroïde pour chaque partie**"

