#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3058
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3161
msgid "The output vector layer of features with only the filtered vertices."
msgstr ""
"Couche vectorielle de sortie d'entités avec uniquement les vertex filtrés."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3064
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:filterverticesbym``"
msgstr "**ID de l'algorithme** : ``native:filterverticesbym``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3074
msgid "Filter vertices by Z value"
msgstr "Filtrer les vertex par valeur Z"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3075
msgid ""
"Filters away vertices based on their Z value, returning geometries with only"
" vertex points that have a Z value greater than or equal to the specified "
"minimum value and/or less than or equal to the maximum value."
msgstr ""
"Filtre les sommets en fonction de leur valeur Z, renvoyant des géométries "
"avec uniquement des points ou sommets ayant une valeur Z supérieure ou égale"
" à la valeur minimale spécifiée et/ou inférieure ou égale à la valeur "
"maximale."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3087
msgid ""
"The red line represents the black line with only vertices whose Z value is "
"<=10."
msgstr ""
"La ligne rouge représente la ligne noire avec uniquement des sommets dont la"
" valeur Z est <= 10."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3099
msgid ""
":ref:`qgisfilterverticesbym`, :ref:`qgisextractvertices`, "
":ref:`qgisextractspecificvertices`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`qgisfilterverticesbym`, :ref:`qgisextractvertices`, "
":ref:`qgisextractspecificvertices`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3126
msgid "Minimum of Z values allowed"
msgstr "Minimum de valeurs Z autorisées"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3134
msgid "Maximum of Z values allowed"
msgstr "Maximum de valeurs Z autorisées"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3167
