#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7082
msgid "Tessellate"
msgstr "Tessellate"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7083
msgid ""
"Tessellates a polygon geometry layer, dividing the geometries into "
"triangular components."
msgstr ""
"une couche mosaïque de géométrie polygonale, divisant les géométries en "
"composants triangulaires."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7086
msgid ""
"The output layer consists of multipolygon geometries for each input feature,"
" with each multipolygon consisting of multiple triangle component polygons."
msgstr ""
"La couche de sortie se compose de géométries multipolygones pour chaque "
"entité en entrée, chaque multipolygone étant composé de plusieurs polygones "
"triangulaires."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7093
msgid "Tessellated polygon (right)"
msgstr "Polygone en mosaïque (à droite)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7115
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7139
msgid "**Tesselated**"
msgstr "**Mosaïqué**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7142
